name: Consulting Services
description:
144th & Vine; LLC is a Life Consulting agency that offers individual or group consulting services to youth or adults, who are ready to Walk in their Purpose & Live out their Destinies!

Through one on one sessions, We inspire and equip our consumers to embrace the Third Metric and define their own success in the area of their choosing. Be it College or Career Readiness, starting your own business or planning a family; One of our consultants can meet your needs.

name: Workshop/Speaker
description:

Hosting an inspirational speaker is one way to jump-start a communityâ€™s desire to seek opportunities in a world where so many people suffer from abject poverty and oppression. For schools and graduations, this presentation motivates scholars to overcome their adversities and not become products of their environment.
